snippet.title: Ankh Speed Run
snippet.description:
ANKH or 64 Rooms: An Adventure in the Metareal World

by David Van Brink was published in 1984. In 2011, youtube user PHYNNBOI uploaded this C64-emulated play-through of the game.

But it's not just a play-through... it is a speed run. PHYNNBOI knows all the tricks, has carefully 100%'d all the objects, has mastered all the timings.

You can play this game in your browser, thanks to archive.org: https://archive.org/details/a2_Ankh_1984_Datamost_cr_2

Phynnboi's original video upload is
part 1: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=he-L9...
part 2: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TqLO3...

Thank you @phynnboi!
